snippet.title: Wolfenstein | Blade of Agony Chapter 3 - Comparison between 2015 and 2020 and why did it even start?
snippet.description:
In this developer video of 'Blade of Agony' Chapter 3, the project lead Daniel 'Tormentor667' talks about the differences between the release in 2015 (from the start to 07:08) and the currently in development 2020 version of the game (from 07:08 to the end) - mostly comparing the very first mission.

Get some insight information about what the team is doing to improve the overall experience and how the game even started, it's worth it, it's exciting and it's full of grammar mistakes and an ugly german voiceover ;)
